{
  "texts": [
    "Haomo (Ma et al. 2022): This dataset was collected in urban environments of Beijing by a mobile robot built by HAOMO.AI Technology company equipped with a HESAI Pan-darXT 32-beam LiDAR sensor, a SENSING-SG2 wide-angle camera, and an ASENSING-INS570D RTK GNSS.",
    "There are currently five sequences: seq 1-1 and 1-2 were collected from the same route on 8th December 2021 with opposite driving directions.",
    "An additional seq 1-3 from the same route is utilized as the online query with respect to both 1-1 and 1-2 respectively to evaluate place recognition performance of forward and reverse driving.",
    "Seq 2-1 and 2-2 are collected along a much longer route from the same direction, but on different dates i.e.",
    "28th December 2021 and 13th January 2022, respectively."
  ]
}